articles.author: Brian Flood, Joseph Wulfsohn
articles.title: TikTok will remove calls to read Osama bin Laden's 'Letter to America,” says it 'clearly' promotes terrorism - Fox Business
articles.description: TikTok said Osama bin Laden's infamous pro-terrorism "Letter to America" violates its rules about supporting any form of terrorism and will be removed from the platform.
articles.content:
TikTok will remove videos promoting Osama bin Laden's infamous pro-terrorism "Letter to America," citing violations of its rules on supporting any form of terrorism.
